code: public static String getStateString(int state) {     switch(state) {         case STATE_COMMITTED:             return "committed".         case STATE_ROLLED_BACK:             return "rolled back".         case STATE_MIXED:             return "mixed".         default:             return "unknown".     } }

code: /**  * Return the outcome state of the transaction state,  * as one of the constants in this class.  * @see #STATE_UNKNOWN  * @see #STATE_COMMITTED  * @see #STATE_ROLLED_BACK  * @see #STATE_MIXED  */ public int getOutcomeState() {     return this.outcomeState. }
